# Basics HTML & Page Swapping

This project is part of my frontend learning journey where I practiced basic HTML concepts and implemented simple page navigation.

## Features
- Basic HTML structure (head, body, headings, paragraphs)
- Multiple web pages
- Page navigation using links (page swapping)
- Simple and clean layout

## Files Included
- page1.html
- page2.html

## What I Learned
- How to structure a basic HTML page
- How to connect multiple pages using links
- Understanding of file paths and navigation
- Building a simple multi-page website

## Purpose
This project is created for practice and learning purposes to strengthen my HTML fundamentals.

## Next Step
I will enhance this project using CSS for styling and better user interface.
